<span id="Description"></span>
== Описание ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:Draft_PointLinkArray.svg|24px]] '''Draft PointLinkArray''' command creates a [[App_Link|Link]] array from a selected object by placing copies at the points from a point object. Use the [[Draft_PointArray|Draft PointArray]] command to create a less efficient regular array instead. Except for the type of array that is created, [[App_Link|Link]] array or regular array, this command is identical to the [[Draft_PointArray|Draft PointArray]] command. See there for more information.
</div>


